AWESOME!!!

Trinity::
She was just running out of the CF, trying to catch up with 
Archangle, when she ran into SkyLynk literaly.  She bumped into him 
and fell back.  She looked up at him and took a step back. She was 
scared at first, and it showed. Then she tried to show that she was a 
big bot.  She growled, in her kitten growl, and showed her large 
saber tooth tiger fangs.  She roared in her kitten roar. "Hey, 
where'd you come from? I didn't see you  there.  I hope I didn't hurt 
you." trying to act big. "ah, are you going to the fight too?"
